The paper discusses security risks in sensor measurements, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also mentions the interfaces between sensors and microcontrollers, which relates to embedded systems (cs.ET). The paper discusses the need for improving the security of everyday commodity devices, which could fall under human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the wider context of side-channel leakage and electromagnetic interference, which could fall under systems and control (cs.SY).
